# TenantIsolation.thunder
# Global invariants , system-wide laws that must hold across every feature and service,
# not just one mission. A locally-valid change can still violate a global invariant.

mission MultiTenantPlatform
use product

title "Keep every tenant's data and money strictly isolated and consistent"
for PlatformSecurity

goal
  Serve many tenants from one system without any cross-tenant leak or inconsistency.

why
  A single cross-tenant leak or a lost ledger entry is catastrophic and unrecoverable trust damage.

owner PlatformSecurity

invariant TenantIsolation
  statement one tenant's data is never visible to another tenant
  scope global
  applies_to
    apis
    events
    databases
    caches
    logs
    search
  severity critical
  because the entire multi-tenant promise rests on this one law
  verify tenant isolation property test

invariant CompletedPaymentHasLedgerEntry
  statement every completed payment has exactly one ledger entry
  scope global
  applies_to
    databases
    events
  severity critical
  because a payment with zero or two ledger entries is a financial correctness break
  verify ledger reconciliation test

invariant EveryMutationIsAuthorized
  statement no state-changing request runs without an authorization decision
  scope global
  severity critical
  because an unauthorized mutation is the root of most breaches
  verify authorization coverage test
